description: We fight the first boss Abaddon the early game on the hardest difficulty which is unlocked after beating the full game. On hard mode, enemy shields and health are tankier, and they hit much harder. But we take no damage throughout the fight.
title: Stellar Blade - Hard Mode No Damage Abaddon Boss Gameplay

description:
The Fallout 4 Next Gen update is here. We’ve gone hands on with the game on Xbox Series X, with footage of before the patch on the left and after the patch on the right. While the game has received a resolution increase, and seemingly somewhat improved colors and lighting, what is most noticeable is the framerate increase, even on the quality mode displayed here. You can even set the game to performance mode for increased frames as well. Here are several different comparisons, including slowed down footage, in order to best display the differences.

#gaming #Fallout4 #gamespot
title: Fallout 4 Next Gen Update Comparison
